1.2.0
-----
- pages are generated using StringTemplate library, this allows easier
  template customization
- photo index is generated without tables on album page
- links in album and photo descriptions are parsed and converted
  into html links
- css simplification and improvements
- exif displaying reimplemented using jquery
- idea of multiple image views is discarded (no more preview/view pages)

1.0.2
-----
- fixed execution of third party programs (i.e. ImageMagick/GraphicsMagick)

1.0.1
-----
- allow '-' character in photo and album/subalbum names
- minor bugfixes

1.0.0
-----
- first public release
